Sanjay and Craig - Season 1 - Episode 10 (WEBRip - XviD)

This is the story of two inseparable best friends. Oh, yeah - one's a talking

an old, abandoned robot! Get ready for 20 stories where routine hijinks cross right
over into the land of the hysterically absurd with Sanjay and Craig!
